project.name: Storage Domain v1
project.description:
Moving and storing crates of goods by hoists from containers to depots with spatial maps. "Storage" is a planning domain involving spatial reasoning. Basically, the domain is about moving a certain number of crates from some containers to some depots by hoists. Inside a depot, each hoist can move according to a specified spatial map connecting different areas of the depot. The test problems for this domain involve different numbers of depots, hoists, crates, containers, and depot areas. At the beginning of each problem file, we give the spatial map of the depot areas. While in this domain it is important to generate plans of good quality, for many test problems, even finding any solution can be quite hard for domain-independent planners.
Based on IPC5 Storage Domain (original authors: Alfonso Gerevini and Alessandro Saetti)

actor.name: Hoist
actor.description: This actor is responsible for arranging the crates at a place and loading then in to a truck.

useCase.name: Move from one area to another
useCase.description: The hoist moves from an origin area to a destination area.

definition.precondition: - the truck must at the origin place.
definition.postcondition: - the truck is at the destination place; - the fuel cost is increased.
definition.invariants: - the truck load remains the same.

useCase.name: Lift a crate
useCase.description: The agent hoist lifts a crate from a surface (a pallet or another crate) at a place.

definition.invariants: - the hoist, the crate and the surface remain at the same place.

useCase.name: Drop a crate
useCase.description: The agent hoist drops a crate on a surface (a pallet or another crate) at a place.

definition.postcondition: - the crate is on the surface; - the hoist is available.
definition.invariants: - the hoist, the crate and the surface remain at the same place.

useCase.name: Go inside a area
useCase.description: The hoist go inside a area (storearea).

definition.invariants: - the truck, the crate and the hoist remain at the same place.

useCase.name: Go ouit from a area
useCase.description: The hoist go out from a area (storearea).

definition.invariants: - the truck, the crate and the hoist remain at the same place.

action.precondition: a1.connected->exists(x:Storearea| x = a2) and h.at = a2 and h.lifting = c and a1.clear= true and a1.inside = p
action.postcondition: h.lifting = null and h.available = true and a1.clear = false

action.precondition: a1.connected->exists(x:Storearea| x = a2) and h.available = true and h.at = a2 and a1.inside = p
action.postcondition: a1.clear = true and h.available = false and h.lifting = c

action.precondition: h.at = from and from.connected->exists(x:Area| x = to) and to.clear = true
h.at = from and from.connected->exists(x:Area| x = to)
h.at = from and to.clear = true and from.connected->exists(x:Area| x = to)
action.postcondition: h.at = to and to.clear = false and from.clear = true
